      <title>python的环境配置</title>
      <link href="/2018/10/19/python%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
      <url>/2018/10/19/python%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Python 是一门有条理的和强大的面向对象的程序设计语言，类似于Perl, Ruby, Scheme, Java。</p><blockquote><p>1.首先我们打开<a href="https://www.python.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">python官网:</a></p></blockquote><p><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonh1.jpg" alt="python"></p><p>看到箭头指到的地方，点击下载，这是3.7的版本，也有<a href="https://www.python.org/downloads/windows/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">3.6的版本和其他版本</a>，这是windows上的，如有需要其他mac 和linux 版本以及其他版本，可以上<a href="https://www.python.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">python官网</a>下载，这里就不一一说了。慢慢等待下载，完成后打开安装。</p><blockquote><p>2.勾选 Add python to PATH 添加路径:</p></blockquote><p>  …安装界面点击Customize installation 自定义安装</p><p>  <img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/python%20add.png" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>3.不改变默认进行Next下一步:</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonadd3.png" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>4.选择一个自己喜欢的安装位置:</p></blockquote><p>…点击Install开始安装<br><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonadd4.png" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>5.等待进度条加载完毕:</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonadd5.png" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>6.安装完毕，点击Close关闭:</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonadd6.png" alt=""></p><p>环境配置就算好了，记得添加Add python to PATH,如果你忘了勾选，下面我们就自己手动环境配置。</p><blockquote><p>1,点“我的电脑”，右键选“属性”</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythoh2.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>2.选择“高级系统设置”—&gt;选“环境变量”—&gt;在“系统变量”中选中“Path”,再点“编辑”—&gt;再点“编辑文本”。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonh3.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonh4.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonh5.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>3.新建</p></blockquote><p>   把你刚刚下的的路径(D:\python文件夹下面的python.exe)放在变量值里面，变量名可以取为path，然后点击确定。</p><blockquote><p>4.验证：按下win键+R键打开运行窗口输入cmd并回车：</p></blockquote><p>  切换到d盘:然后输入python-v</p><p><img src="https://deling-1255359399.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/python%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/pythonadd7.png" alt=""></p><p>  如果上面出现这个情况，说明你已经配置好了环境，接下来你就可以继续学习python了！</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
